<details class="mln-runbook">
  <summary>Run your own reading group</summary>
  <div class="mln-runbook-body">
    <p>Take this format — it's all you need to start one in your own city.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Read ahead, or read on the day.</strong> People can read the paper ahead of time, or just show up and read it together during the optional quiet hour before discussion.</li>
      <li><strong>Walk through it section by section.</strong> Go through the paper one section at a time, pausing to ask questions and open up discussion as much as possible.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Questions? <a href="mailto:chrisshi@andrew.cmu.edu">Email me</a>.</p>
  </div>
</details>
